title: 100 Years of Frank Sinatra: A Salute to Sinatra
desc: International vocalist, Gary Grace?has performed the songs of Frank Sinatra all over the world and has recently this year appeared in Minsk, Belarus & the Caribbean. In this, Sinatra's Centenary Year, he will be appearing at Leyton Great Hall performing classic songs such as 'Come Fly With Me', Strangers In The Night', 'Under My Skin', 'That's Life', 'New York', 'Fly Me To The Moon',?'My Way'? and many, many more.  For more information about Gary, visit? www.garygrace.co.uk ? If this event sells out, you can add yourself to the waitlist and you will be contacted if a space becomes available.
